node.text: you graduated kindergarten and you didn’t quit. congratulations baby, you did it. you had ups and you had downs but you always found a way to turn it around. off to first grade you go. i want you to know i love watching you grow. mommys first man, you are a star. i know you’ll grow up to be the best man you already are. i don’t think first grade is ready for you. it’ll be something new that mommy will walk you all the way through. your intelligence, your honesty, your smart little humor. I’m not ready for all the little rumors. but i know you’re tough and a smart young man. mommy will always be your number one fan. I love you my sweet boy. kick first grades butt. @daimonantwonprincejr
